      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWICE AZ COOL (4) recorded a gutsy Maiden victory with the 4kg claiming apprentice aboard over 1200m at Warren on a soft (7) surface. Looks to have a stack of upside and can win again with the claim. Looks well placed to take this out. ZOUCRATIC (1) best performance this prep when taken to the front for a gritty third over 1250m at Gunnedah. Rinse and repeat today and can break through. FLIRTATION (2) well bred Snitzel filly who bounced off her sound debut second, with a dominant on-speed win over 900m at Scone in fast time. Sticky gate again but has the upside to put these away. DEVILISH SUN (3) comes here in peak condition after getting off the mark over 1200m at Moree. Drawn to stalk the speed and can take a hand in the finish in this stronger contest.",
